      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh okay good to know. i was getting kind of worried. you think if i just drink extra water and keep going itll settle down? i dont really want to go back to the doctors unless it gets super bad because the co-pay is annoying. if i just take a little less tonight just to settle my stomach that would be okay right?",
