    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay i'll try to keep the dose the same then. my friend was actually saying that if the nausea keeps up i should probably take more ibuprofen to help with the stomach upset so it doesnt bother me as much while i'm adjusting. is that a safe thing to do with the lithium or should i avoid it?",
